Interrupt Technology Corporation

This is the home page of Interrupt Technology Corporation. If you are looking for another company that calls itself "ITcorp", you'll have to try typing the company's full name into a search engine.

What Do We Do?

We are a small, privately held software consulting firm specializing in file systems, storage systems, and computer measurement. We also provide expert-witness services in those areas. If you have a need for our services, you may contact itcorp at itcorp.com (replacing the "at" with an @ sign).

Why Is This Web Page So Plain?

We do not actively seek outside business. This Web page exists primarily to satisfy the needs of those who expect every domain to have a Web presence.
